snippet.title: Mokoko X Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Mokoko X is the enhanced remake version of Mokoko. The game will be released on Steam, Switch (April 7th 2022), Xbox One (April 22th 2022). 
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1785000/Mokoko_X
Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/mokoko-x-switch/
Xbox: https://www.xbox.com/en-us/games/store/mokoko-x/9pgjk7m3p4rp
